<h1>Beta Version</h1>
<p>
    This is an unoficial Loot Generator for 2K and Nerdvana Games <a href="https://nerdvanagames.myshopify.com/">Bunkers and Badasses</a> TTRPG Game. 
    All of the data has been painstakingly transcribed by hand from the Book, to avoid having to stop the game just to generate loot.
</p>
<p>Right click on a card to download it or copy it to your clipboard. You do you!
In order to enable this in Firefox you'll need to the <b>dom.events.asyncClipboard.clipboardItem</b> 
preferences (needs to be set to true). To change preferences in Firefox, visit about:config.
</p>


